deo></span><br><strong>经营好主城，目标就是击退外敌、开疆拓土！体验经典的大地图“涂色”征服与卡牌战斗，并可抓捕敌将首领进行调教劝降，将其纳入麾下。带领大宋重现辉煌。剧情党可解锁丰富叙事线，探索阵营间的恩怨情仇</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/c93e4012ddad67971346a7acf58c0ba0.avif?t=1771073864\" width=615 height=73 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/9014751dbef266e0aeda83788beea95c.poster.avif?t=1771073864\" width=614 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/9014751dbef266e0aeda83788beea95c.webm?t=1771073864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/9014751dbef266e0aeda83788beea95c.mp4?t=1771073864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>当城主内外兼顾，自然少不了一段温暖的相伴。游戏内置多位可攻略女性角色，支持深度互动与专属剧情，甚至可解锁生子系统，为争霸之路增添人情温度</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/4ed3a1b9e3ed1518f3faf045d70c36de.avif?t=1771073864\" width=615 height=73 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/3e53baebce5bace108cba516303e14f1.poster.avif?t=1771073864\" width=614 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/3e53baebce5bace108cba516303e14f1.webm?t=1771073864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/3e53baebce5bace108cba516303e14f1.mp4?t=1771073864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>内置随机装备系统，每次掉落都暗藏惊喜，助力战力突破；涂色块式大地图直观清晰，搭配完善的运输系统与据点管理机制，让你在金、宋、西夏、大理四大阵营的争霸中，体验从零到一的疆域扩张快感</strong><br><br><strong>后续内容值得期待</strong><br>未来将深度打磨国家系统与阵营外交机制，新增基于将领特性的计策系统，进一步丰富策略维度，带来更完整的争霸体验<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209930/extras/48be0bc758afbe133e9d7c579104dedc.avif?t=1771073864\" width=614 height=184 /></span>",
